The '''Kwuennox Smugglers''' were a team of [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] in the times of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. They were commanded by [[Ozik Poyiu]].

The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] decimated the Kwuennox Smugglers. After that, the survivors, including Poyiu, joined the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. Poyiu reformed the Smugglers to create the [[Gale Team]].

